Upstream attribution for `scientific-agent-tools`

This plugin was bootstrapped from material derived from:

https://github.com/ed3dai/ed3d-plugins/tree/main/plugins/ed3d-extending-claude

The Scientific Software Playbook version adapts that material for:
- plugin-scoped source-of-truth paths under `plugins/`
- Codex global-install behavior under `CODEX_HOME`
- AGENTS-first repository context maintenance
- current runtime-compatibility sync and contract-check flows

See `LICENSE` in this directory for the license applied to this plugin bundle.
